  <!-- Short Bio Philosophy Section -->
  <section aria-labelledby="about-heading" class="border-t border-border-subtle pt-12 max-w-[800px] mx-auto">
    <h2 id="about-heading" class="text-2xl font-bold text-text-primary tracking-tight mb-6">
      My Journey
    </h2>
    <div class="text-text-secondary space-y-6 leading-[1.75]">
      <p>
          My first experiences with computers start all the way back in the 90's with a Gateway PC, Windows 95, and shortly after using the AOL web browser on a dial-up connection. Floppy disks were still being used and were slowly being replaced by CDs.
      </p>
      <p>
          Fast forward to 2014 when I took an "Intro to Web Development" course as an elective and learned to build web pages with HTML and CSS. I very much enjoyed the idea
      </p>
      <p>
        My core philosophy centers on <strong class="text-text-primary font-medium">zero-overhead abstractions</strong> and <strong class="text-text-primary font-medium">radical simplicity</strong>. I believe developer tooling should be invisible yet incredibly fast, and that software complexity should only be introduced when there is no other path forward. When I build, I optimize for the end-user experience and developer feedback loops alike.
      </p>
      <p>
        Whether it's building Sentinel CI to shave 15 minutes off every build, implementing local-first collaborative sync inside SyncSpace, or compiling component styles at build time, I tackle bottlenecks from first principles.
      </p>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- Most Recent Posts Section -->
  {% if collections.posts and collections.posts.length > 0 %}
  <section aria-labelledby="blog-heading" class="border-t border-border-subtle pt-12">
    <div class="flex items-center justify-between mb-8">
      <div>
        <h2 id="blog-heading" class="text-2xl font-bold text-text-primary tracking-tight">
          Recent Posts
        </h2>
        <p class="text-sm text-text-muted mt-2">
            Documenting my thoughts and experiences in the world of building software with AI agents.
        </p>
      </div>
      <a href="/blog/" class="text-sm font-semibold text-accent-light hover:text-accent transition-colors duration-200 flex items-center gap-1">
        <span>All Posts</span>
        <span>&rarr;</span>
      </a>
    </div>

    <!-- 3-Column Grid -->
    <div class="grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-2 lg:grid-cols-3 gap-6">
      {% set recent_posts = collections.posts | reverse %}
      {% for post in recent_posts %}
        {% if loop.index0 < 3 %}
          {% include "components/blog-card.njk" %}
        {% endif %}
      {% endfor %}
    </div>
  </section>
  {% endif %}

  <!-- Contact Section -->
  {% include "components/contact.njk" %}
</div>
